Whenever you feel
your mind racing & ruminating
do the 5-5-5 Breathing Exercise:

♻️Breathe in - counting to 5.
♻️Hold your breath - counting to 5.
♻️Breathe out - counting to 5.

Repeat 10 times.

This oxygenates your body
which in turn signals your brain
that “Everything’s OK”.
